column4: i have a problem with a kernel in fedora and i know you guys do not care but the thing is the same thing works in ubuntu so my wonder is WHY. It is a PCIe RME RayDat card and it gets recognized in ubuntu but in fedora 14 lspci gives me "Unkown header type 7f". What is that?
